WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.583
I spill out of my name like light through broken water.

00:00:06.200 --> 00:00:10.117
Every face enters me now; I cannot end at skin.

00:00:13.800 --> 00:00:19.133
The center opens, and a thousand silent suns breathe through it.

00:00:21.200 --> 00:00:26.283
Nothing is mine, so everything flowers inside this vanishing.

